Description: Limestone ostracon: on the recto eight incomplete lines, with red verse points, of a hymn to Thoth as a creator god. On the verso seven incomplete lines of an unidentified literary text (continuation of the hymn?).
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (393739) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/393739)
Previous owner: Previous owner/ex-collection: Norman de Garis Davies
